transcript: So I've had a high fever for five to seven days now. I feel pain in my joints, my lymphatic nodes are pretty swollen too. It doesn't, I don't really feel good most of the day. I can't get on my bed. I just feel very sick overall. I have some chills as well, and I'm experiencing some night sweats. The fever comes and goes but it's been persistent. I'm also feeling quite fatigued and have lost my appetite.
